                </a>
            </li>
            <li class="mr-5">
                <a href="#">
                    <svg 
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" 
                    viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor" 
                    class="h-6 w-6 text-slate-400" 
                    aria-hidden="true">
